text: D.C. Cab is a 1983 American comedy movie. It was also known as Street Fleet. The movie was directed by Joel Schumacher. It stars Max Gail, Adam Baldwin, Mr. T, Gary Busey, and Marsha Warfield. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * * Category:1983 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Joel Schumacher Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies set in Washington, D.C.
